Class Dawg

    IFinalFunction<DawgNode>, ITransitionFunction<DawgNode>, Serializable, Iterable<String>, Collection<String>, Set<String>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SortedDawg

    public abstract class Dawg
extends AbstractSet<String>
implements IFinalFunction<DawgNode>, ITransitionFunction<DawgNode>, Serializable
    Provides common logic for all my Dawg implementations. Currently, there is only the SortedDawg implementation, but I have plans for other kinds.

    2.1.0
